author: jsdelfino
msg: Added template for a Subversion configuration file containing the correct property configuration for commonly used file types. Using this configuration will allow correct handling of eol characters in text files on Linux, Mac-OS and Windows platform as well as handling of Rev and Date subversion keywords in these files. On Linux the Subversion configuration file is /home/delfinoj/.subversion/config.
